      <title>乍得的非公开选举让领导人与自己的总理对决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/chad-s-closed-election-pits-leader-against-own-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乍得临时总统穆罕默德·代比在其父亲去世后掌权，目前正在与总理竞选最高职位，这引发了人们对他没有真正反对派的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/chad-s-closed-election-pits-leader-against-own-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 20:27:27 GMT</pubDate>
